  "facts": [
    {
      "section": "<known section>",
      "key": "<stable key>",
      "value": <JSON value>,
      "locator": "<paragraph or line reference>",
      "confidence": <0..1>
    }
  ],
  "gap_signals": [
    {
      "section": "<section>",
      "kind": "missing|ambiguous|conflict|low_confidence|unsupported",
      "message": "<short reason>"
    }
  ]
}
```

Use sections from `WIKI_SCHEMA.md` and obligations from `LEGAL_MAP.md`. When
unsure, emit a `low_confidence` gap signal rather than guessing.

